<title>yǒu yī tiān wǒ men yào dào 迦南723</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu yī tiān wǒ men yào dào tiān de nà yī biān. yǒu yī tiān wǒ men yào dào nà biān dà tuán yuán.
 yǒu yī tiān wǒ men yào dà zàn měi, zhí dào yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn.
 hā lì lù yà róng yào guī gěi yé sū jī dū. hā lì lù yà róng yào, tā yǐ zhǎng wáng quán.
 róng yào róng yào\001yǒng yǒng yuǎn yuǎn, wǒ men yào dà tuán yuán.</lyrics>
</song>